{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But remember also, that we're talking about age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When do you defy your parents is the question of-- of growing up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When did I-- but when I defied my-- my father, it was in his own image, strangely as it may-- strange as it may be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- we had Passover at home, always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "High Holidays, you're referring to New Year and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father would somehow still need to go to pray.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he wouldn't pray in the regular-- regular synagogue because he didn't belong to any.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they would rent-- actually it was the Lodz Philharmonic, which had a-- had a hall where they had performances, theater or mostly orchestra.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would rent that for the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they do that today, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They rent the high school auditorium too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they would rent that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all sell ticket, I guess, or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father would go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, he would find most of his friends, most of the people of the same persuasion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they would come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would pray.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would insist to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One event that I remember distinctly, my father never touched me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- my mother would spank me when I was very little, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother was always quoting her father saying that-- my mother said that you are my only child.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I'm going to raise you as one of eight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so she would.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father would never.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only time he slapped me on my face was once in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's on a Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My cousin took me to the movies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the movie was Mario [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], was the movie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she walked out with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she bought me chocolate.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
